comments: Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Leonard's (LAC) path and does not deliver contact as it occurs to his side.
Craig (PHX) attempts to tie the ball up and marginal arm contact occurs with Leonard (LAC).
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Zubac (LAC).
Leonard (GSW) establishes his left foot as his pivot and maintains it prior to stepping off his right foot to release the pass.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in Leonard's (LAC) path and does not deliver contact as it occurs to his backside.
Leonard (LAC) brings his hand to Durant's (PHX) front and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Leonard (LAC) and Craig (PHX) come together as Craig moves over the pick and marginal contact occurs as Leonard releases away.
Mann (LAC) establishes screening position and does not deliver contact to Craig (PHX) as it occurs to Mann's side.
While attempting to gather the ball, Leonard (LAC) fumbles the ball, any additional contact from Paul (PHX) is consider incidental.
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Leonard (LAC) initiates contact with Paul's (PHX) left arm that impedes his ability to secure the loose ball.
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Craig (PHX) makes contact with Leonard's (LAC) forearm prior to the release of his jump shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) deflects the ball OOB. Possession is correctly retained by LAC.
Zubac (LAC) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Ayton (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Zubac (LAC).
Mann (LAC) and Ayton (PHX) both make contact with the ball prior to incidental hand to hand contact occurring thereafter during the rebound.
The ball goes OOB off Craig's (PHX) left foot. Possession is correctly retained by LAC.
Paul (PHX) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Booker (PHX) makes contact with Westbrook (LAC) that affects his shot attempt in the post.
Paul (PHX) is awarded a timeout prior to 5 seconds elapsing during the in-bound.
Leonard (LAC) rests his arm across Durant's (PHX) back during the in-bounds play and marginal contact occurs before Durant releases away.
Gordon (LAC) briefly rests his arm on Shamet's (PHX) opposite side hip during the in-bounds play and marginal contact occurs before Shamet releases away.
Westbrook (LAC) makes contact with the ball prior to incidental "high-five" contact occurring with Booker's (PHX) left hand after release of the driving shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) is in the lane for at or about three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Booker (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes OOB. Possession is correctly awarded to LAC.
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Gordon (LAC).
Booker (PHX) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps prior to releasing his shot attempt.
The game is stopped due to a game clock malfunction. After communicating with the Replay Center, the game clock is ruled to have expired and the game correctly ends.
